Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一日旅行约会 抽插不停旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是久违的约会日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等了很久 而且又忘带手机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆直接去找好美 没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都九点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又赖床了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们好久没见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果一直睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到今天跟你约会就很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整晚似乎没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么久没见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在我家里呆着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白白浪费一次约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了 本来想做早饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 你吃了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都还没吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没见面了 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看胸部会害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一直摸那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别一直看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看胸部吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的胸部很小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次在这里被你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳沟都露出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面好吵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一早就很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好粗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以脱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次在这么亮的地方做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛吗？不会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗？这样会痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样是会痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想插进来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以亲亲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.09,0:25:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最爱你了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.07,0:26:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.12,0:27:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.16,0:28:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.11,0:28:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.13,0:28:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.07,0:28:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射出来多点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.03,0:29:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.13,0:29:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干净了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.07,0:30:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.15,0:30:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.03,0:30:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.12,0:30:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先来冲水
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.06,0:31:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.14,0:31:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来洗澡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.04,0:31:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲水
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.13,0:32:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要洗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.13,0:33:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒好像又变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.07,0:33:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擦身体
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.09,0:33:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.09,0:33:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.12,0:34:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.13,0:34:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.04,0:35:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗？昨晚在睡前
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.05,0:35:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了旅行杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.12,0:35:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想去很大的露天温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.12,0:35:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想去泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.13,0:35:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.07,0:35:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.11,0:36:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.07,0:36:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.03,0:37:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.10,0:37:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次也尽量让你舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.11,0:37:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.11,0:37:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是有点
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.05,0:37:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又做了什么吗？我很认真哦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.06,0:37:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.08,0:38:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.13,0:41:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.14,0:41:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.07,0:41:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大浴场里面好好享受泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.14,0:41:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.15,0:41:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.15,0:41:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发去温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.09,0:41:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违的约会 变成温泉旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.04,0:41:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.11,0:41:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要过夜 觉得好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.04,0:41:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天终于做爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.12,0:42:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.06,0:42:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.09,0:42:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.10,0:42:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不是旅馆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.10,0:42:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉那里好像有点
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.04,0:42:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.05,0:43:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那里做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.05,0:43:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.06,0:43:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像是来偷情的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.13,0:43:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要去旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.07,0:43:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有浴缸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.14,0:43:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想一起泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.08,0:43:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把浴场包下了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.09,0:43:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包下了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.16,0:43:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.16,0:43:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得一起出来就想好好单独泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.03,0:43:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要过夜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.04,0:43:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.11,0:44:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅馆吗？不是温泉住宿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.05,0:44:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.12,0:44:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我都没感觉累
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.06,0:44:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息吗？那休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.08,0:44:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.08,0:44:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用摄像机拍摄吗？你带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.15,0:44:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.15,0:44:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以重温回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.09,0:44:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想拍
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.09,0:44:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.09,0:44:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.10,0:45:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概这样
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.11,0:45:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.11,0:45:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.11,0:45:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.12,0:45:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.12,0:45:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别一直往下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.13,0:45:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.08,0:45:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.15,0:45:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.05,0:46:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要休息吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.12,0:46:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影机
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.12,0:46:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没拍过 感觉很难
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.14,0:46:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.14,0:46:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要去旅馆休息一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.15,0:47:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那间旅馆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.16,0:47:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也会有旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.10,0:47:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准时前往旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.11,0:47:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到旅馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.04,0:47:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开车有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.05,0:47:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以来休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.13,0:47:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.07,0:47:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.15,0:48:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么突然就摸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.05,0:48:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.13,0:48:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.08,0:49:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.09,0:49:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.16,0:49:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把眼睛闭上
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.05,0:49:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹真的别闹
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.16,0:50:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别突然袭击 我胆子小
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.12,0:50:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.12,0:50:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.06,0:51:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影机还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.06,0:51:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.10,0:52:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 又突然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.05,0:53:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别玩内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.07,0:53:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都只有我脱 好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.15,0:53:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪拿出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.09,0:53:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那个对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.16,0:53:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会动对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.11,0:54:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个振动好像很强
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.05,0:54:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.06,0:54:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很强 我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.09,0:54:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.05,0:55:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.06,0:55:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己不太会
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.14,0:55:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.07,0:55:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.11,0:56:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.11,0:56:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.13,0:56:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.13,0:56:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样用的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.15,0:56:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.08,0:57:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.03,0:57:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好强
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.10,0:57:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.11,0:57:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.13,0:57:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛笑
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.14,0:57:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.14,0:57:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.08,0:58:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.15,0:58:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛一直笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.04,0:58:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别玩那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.06,0:58:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.06,0:58:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.13,0:58:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.14,0:58:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.07,0:59:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.16,0:59:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.13,0:59:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.16,1:00:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.10,1:00:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.06,1:01:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好玩
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.06,1:01:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不行
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.05,1:01:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太久了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.05,1:02:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心 很厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.13,1:02:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.13,1:02:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.13,1:02:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也可以弄男生吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.14,1:02:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能女生吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.08,1:02:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点 男生不会舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.15,1:02:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会哦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.08,1:02:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.09,1:02:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.11,1:02:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗？舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.04,1:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是弄这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.05,1:03:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.12,1:03:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.06,1:03:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄哪边 要弄哪边才舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.06,1:03:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗？舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.13,1:03:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.14,1:03:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴吗？再用嘴巴吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.08,1:03:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你不能跑哦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.11,1:04:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有味道
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.11,1:04:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.07,1:04:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.10,1:05:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.05,1:05:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.05,1:05:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我舔哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.14,1:05:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.14,1:05:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.08,1:05:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像会痛 不会吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.04,1:06:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没生气
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.07,1:06:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.16,1:07:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.16,1:08:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来拿吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.04,1:08:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进来 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.13,1:08:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.14,1:09:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.10,1:09:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.14,1:10:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.15,1:10:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 忘了这个吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.09,1:10:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能玩
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.05,1:10:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.15,1:11:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.12,1:12:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.05,1:12:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.07,1:12:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.07,1:12:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服 很开心
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.08,1:12:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在换我动吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.09,1:12:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.05,1:13:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？好幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.05,1:13:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最爱你啦
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.06,1:14:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.07,1:14:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换后面吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.09,1:14:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我动吗？可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.05,1:15:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.12,1:15:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.06,1:15:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.12,1:16:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.09,1:17:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.16,1:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.15,1:18:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.16,1:18:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛打我
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.12,1:18:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.14,1:18:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.04,1:19:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最爱你了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.10,1:20:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.11,1:20:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.06,1:21:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.14,1:21:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.14,1:21:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你舔干净
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.08,1:21:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.04,1:21:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最爱你
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.14,1:22:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里只是休息吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.14,1:22:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走吗？去温泉旅馆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.08,1:22:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该出发了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.08,1:22:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍事休息后终于抵达温泉旅馆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.10,1:22:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.04,1:22:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多条路
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.11,1:23:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪条？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.12,1:23:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有预订房间吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.12,1:23:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一条
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.06,1:23:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.06,1:23:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走哪条？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.07,1:23:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走这看看
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.09,1:23:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.16,1:23:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.10,1:23:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里应该就是
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.13,1:24:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.14,1:24:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的房间 好有古早味
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.15,1:24:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有暖炉
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.09,1:24:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.11,1:25:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 休息一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.12,1:25:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.12,1:25:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要洗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.08,1:25:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴巾
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.09,1:25:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.16,1:25:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换浴衣
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.16,1:26:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去泡澡
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.10,1:26:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好可爱 粉红色
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.04,1:26:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢这件
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.12,1:26:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.12,1:26:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好看吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.06,1:26:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.13,1:26:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.07,1:26:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.08,1:26:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.08,1:26:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你又做什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.09,1:27:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 去泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.09,1:27:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.16,1:27:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.16,1:27:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.04,1:27:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.11,1:27:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.08,1:28:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.15,1:28:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.09,1:28:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕弄脏浴衣了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.16,1:28:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 当做没发生
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.10,1:28:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澡堂在哪
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.05,1:28:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉要买新的丝袜
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.13,1:28:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走哪边？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.08,1:29:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.09,1:29:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看着我一直笑
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.16,1:29:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没搞笑
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.04,1:29:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边是浴池吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.12,1:29:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.12,1:29:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒哦 很大
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.13,1:29:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们两个
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.07,1:30:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整间包了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.14,1:30:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就赶快泡吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.08,1:30:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吗 来
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.09,1:30:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以先去
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.16,1:30:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我待会过去
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.04,1:30:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会拉坏
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.12,1:30:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.05,1:30:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你先去的话 我会很感激
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.07,1:31:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.14,1:31:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.08,1:31:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.16,1:31:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也准备吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.09,1:31:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很难做
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.04,1:31:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.05,1:31:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴巾
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.13,1:32:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拿毛巾
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.07,1:32:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾别
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.14,1:32:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.09,1:32:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会拉坏
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.16,1:32:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去吗？快点
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.04,1:32:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己真的可以
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.13,1:33:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.14,1:33:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好宽敞
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.08,1:33:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温度如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.14,1:33:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温度
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.15,1:33:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.04,1:34:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没胖吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.12,1:34:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.13,1:34:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.12,1:35:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泡澡好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.07,1:35:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.15,1:35:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里都是山 有很多岛吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.04,1:36:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.14,1:36:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.12,1:37:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来泡澡的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.05,1:37:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.06,1:37:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是很害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.17,1:38:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
